    "description": "<strong>专为 VR 打造。回忆在这里更近。</strong><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Hidden Memories of The Gardens Between</i> 是一款关于时间、记忆和友谊的宁静的单人冒险益智游戏。Hidden Memories 的内容是原版的两倍，邀请您解锁 Arina 的个人日记并解决 40 多个新谜题——自然融入更深入、更亲密的旅程。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3084870/extras/1903a442893eb113f64fac66e750c6e0.poster.avif?t=1758077750\" width=450 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3084870/extras/1903a442893eb113f64fac66e750c6e0.webm?t=1758077750\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3084870/extras/1903a442893eb113f64fac66e750c6e0.mp4?t=1758077750\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Hidden Memories 的新内容</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🧩 40 多个新谜题——专为 VR 设计的令人愉悦的创意谜题。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🎨 充满活力的艺术风格——美丽的、受故事书启发的岛屿，您现在可以亲自前往参观。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🌟 扩展的获奖叙事——深入了解 Arina 的插图日记，获得新的见解与视角。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >✨ 异想天开的 VR 互动——通过直观、亲手操作的游戏方式加深您与故事的联系。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🌌 舒适地沉浸其中——在宁静的岛屿上放松身心，无论坐着或站着，没有压力、失败条件或复杂的用户界面。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3084870/extras/96c4c2b644fdb3f18830b126eb78f9a2.poster.avif?t=1758077750\" width=450 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3084870/extras/96c4c2b644fdb3f18830b126eb78f9a2.webm?t=1758077750\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3084870/extras/96c4c2b644fdb3f18830b126eb78f9a2.mp4?t=1758077750\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>游戏玩法</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >控制时间本身来解决由记忆的情感结构构建的谜题。用您的双手移动时间，梦幻般的岛屿在你面前旋转——每一个都是雕刻的记忆，由塑造 Arina 和 Frendt 的过去的情感和物体构建而成。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >⏳ 操纵时间来解决谜题并到达每个岛屿的顶峰。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🎮 玩复古电子游戏、挥动画笔、在博物馆挖掘恐龙骨骼。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🧸 与物体互动来解决谜题——从童年玩具到自我表达的象征性工具。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🌙 探索超现实的梦境，每个细节都承载着情感的重量。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >☑️ 大多数玩家的游戏时间：约 4–8 小时，具体取决于您的解谜熟练度。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3084870/extras/169c18c0fc5392fe3c581727248ff787.poster.avif?t=1758077750\" width=450 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3084870/extras/169c18c0fc5392fe3c581727248ff787.webm?t=1758077750\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3084870/extras/169c18c0fc5392fe3c581727248ff787.mp4?t=1758077750\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>叙述</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过 Arina 不断演变的日记，感受童年纽带在成长过程中微妙的、有时苦乐参半的变化。每个岛屿都捕捉着一个转折点、一种感受或一个被遗忘的时刻——以生动的色彩和纹理呈现。探索记忆、成长以及人与人之间空间的主题。</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过 Arina 的日记和艺术演变深入了解这个故事。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索定义他们友谊并永远改变他们的时刻。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >以新的视角看待过去，在这个既能被感受也能被看见的世界中。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3084870/extras/4b0d9c2ac49e551bda21b0febb909797.poster.avif?t=1758077750\" width=450 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3084870/extras/4b0d9c2ac49e551bda21b0febb909797.webm?t=1758077750\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3084870/extras/4b0d9c2ac49e551bda21b0febb909797.mp4?t=1758077750\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>荣誉</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >荣获 14 项大奖，包括：“年度最佳游戏”奖、韦比奖“最佳谜题”奖和“苹果设计奖”，以及 IGF“视觉艺术卓越奖”等 20 多项国际提名。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《Hidden Memories》（VR）获得媒体好评：Gaming Trend 9/10、 8/10、GeekGasm 8/10、The VR Realm 8.5/10、Use A Potion 8/10、IndieGames.eu 8.5/10、PixelByteGaming 7.5/10、MKAU Gaming 8.5/10。</p></li></ul>",
